{"tid":613033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登同名校成班小朋友打交打上高登搵大人幫手","createTime":"2018-04-01T10:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T14:48:59.000Z","uid":100150,"like":214,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc5d5a99c8ab5b8a9874c1af70c973ce7d91fff","tid":613033,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"透過 HKG 分享一則貼文: 我係名校secret 其中一位admin 希望各位高登仔唔好理班on9仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6882654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6882654&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8bc2468c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6882654</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文: 四月一日夜晚八點向名校secret開戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6882273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6882273&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=dca2701a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6882273</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下入面嘅評論先精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/181421_0a55b5b70becd921cbdb74198ed18dee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F181421_0a55b5b70becd921cbdb74198ed18dee.png&h=e3ebc5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下麻鬼娘娘呢番說話真係精警<br />\n平時又好有骨氣要高登點死點收皮<br />\n兩派平時又稱兄道弟，今日做乜又要上高登搵援兵狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次真係經典作，香港網絡史最精彩嘅大戰，花生愈食愈好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59414b4b902